title: (PC) Life is Feudal Your Own (0.2.3.1)
description:
Life is Feudal: Your Own v0.2.3.1

You must run steam first before launching the game (for more safety use another steam account with no purchased games on it)

Run yo_cm_client.exe

From the main menu press Alt + Z to join the server.

OR

You can also connect to another public server. Open console by pressing 
CTRL + ~ 
and write

joinToRemoteServer("SERVER_IP_ADRESS:28000")

If you see CR_INVALID_VERSION message, you need update your game to the last version.

Check our server group for more details
